snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 43 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 10th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3767 - Bhide To Leave Gokuldham?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu)

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 44 Teaser - 10th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 44 Teaser - 10th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: NATURAL JUICE | Red Tender Coconut Sarbath | Healthy Juice Making in Village | Summer Health Drinks
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we make our village traditional sarbath juice with farm-fresh King Coconut! Tender Coconut water is most effective in summer season. King Coconut variant is a very rare variant than a normal coconut!

We add basil seeds and King coconut meat to make this juice as healthy drink! The taste is divine!

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3765 - Tapu Proposes To Sonu At Lovers Park?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

About MalaimurasuNews TV

Malaimurasu TV (Tamil: மாலைமுரசு ) is a 24x7 live news channel in Tamil launched on Jun 09, 2016. Due to its independent editorial stance it became extremely popular in India and abroad within days of its launch and continues to remain so till date.The channel looks at issues through the eyes of the common man and serves as a platform that airs people's views.The editorial policy is built on strong ethics and fair reporting methods that does not favour or oppose any individual, ideology, group, government, organisation or sponsor.The channel’s primary aim is taking unbiased and accurate information to the socially conscious common man.
Besides giving live and current information the channel broadcasts news on sports,  business and international affairs. It also offers a wide array of week end programmes.
The company also publishes popular Malaimurasu Newspaper & Tamil magazines - Kanmani and Ponmani.

snippet.title: Moment former Pakistan PM Imran Khan is arrested
snippet.description:
Imran Khan, the former prime minister of Pakistan, has been arrested by the military as he appeared in court in Islamabad to face charges in a corruption case. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ► http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

Fawad Chaudhry, a senior official with Khan’s Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf party, said the 72-year-old was arrested on Tuesday by agents from the National Accountability Bureau, the country’s anti-corruption body. A Reuters witness said that shortly after Khan entered through the gate of the Islamabad high court, contingents of paramilitary forces and armoured personnel carriers entered after him.

snippet.title: Oppenheimer | New Trailer
snippet.description:
Oppenheimer - Only In Theaters 7 21 23

Written and directed by Christopher Nolan, Oppenheimer is an IMAX®-shot epic thriller that thrusts audiences into the pulse-pounding paradox of the enigmatic man who must risk destroying the world in order to save it. 
 
The film stars Cillian Murphy as J. Robert Oppenheimer and Emily Blunt as his wife, biologist and botanist Katherine “Kitty” Oppenheimer. Oscar® winner Matt Damon portrays General Leslie Groves Jr., director of the Manhattan Project, and Robert Downey, Jr. plays Lewis Strauss, a founding commissioner of the U.S. Atomic Energy Commission. 
 
Academy Award® nominee Florence Pugh plays psychiatrist Jean Tatlock, Benny Safdie plays theoretical physicist Edward Teller, Michael Angarano plays Robert Serber and Josh Hartnett plays pioneering American nuclear scientist Ernest Lawrence.
 
Oppenheimer also stars Oscar® winner Rami Malek and reunites Nolan with eight-time Oscar® nominated actor, writer and filmmaker Kenneth Branagh. 
 
The cast includes Dane DeHaan (Valerian and the City of a Thousand Planets), Dylan Arnold (Halloween franchise), David Krumholtz (The Ballad of Buster Scruggs), Alden Ehrenreich (Solo: A Star Wars Story) and Matthew Modine (The Dark Knight Rises). 
 
The film is based on the Pulitzer Prize-winning book American Prometheus: The Triumph and Tragedy of J. Robert Oppenheimer by Kai Bird and the late Martin J. Sherwin. The film is produced by Emma Thomas, Atlas Entertainment’s Charles Roven and Christopher Nolan. 

Oppenheimer is filmed in a combination of IMAX® 65mm and 65mm large-format film photography including, for the first time ever, sections in IMAX® black and white analogue photography. 

Nolan’s films, including Tenet, Dunkirk, Interstellar, Inception and The Dark Knight trilogy, have earned more than $5 billion at the global box office and have been awarded 11 Oscars and 36 nominations, including two Best Picture nominations.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3767 - 10 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3767: Problem Kya Hai?
--------------------------------------------------------
After receiving a call from Bhide with some bizarre news, Jetha becomes apprehensive. Jetha visits Taarak at his residence after arriving a little early from work in Gokhuldham. Jetha asks Taarak to be there at his house when Bhide comes to tell him the news. To hear Bhide's news, the entire neighborhood congregates at Gada's home. Additionally, Bhide and Madhavi get ready to travel to Jetha's home. Everyone is waiting for Bhide to make his declaration. What would Bhide be trying to tell Jetha? Follow along to discover more!

snippet.title: MEG 2: THE TRENCH - OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
They’re back for seconds. #Meg2 only in theaters August 4.

Get ready for the ultimate adrenaline rush this summer in “Meg 2: The Trench,” a literally larger-than-life thrill ride that supersizes the 2018 blockbuster and takes the action to higher heights and even greater depths with multiple massive Megs and so much more! Dive into uncharted waters with Jason Statham and global action icon Wu Jing as they lead a daring research team on an exploratory dive into the deepest depths of the ocean. Their voyage spirals into chaos when a malevolent mining operation threatens their mission and forces them into a high-stakes battle for survival. Pitted against colossal Megs and relentless environmental plunderers, our heroes must outrun, outsmart, and outswim their merciless predators in a pulse-pounding race against time. Immerse yourself in the most electrifying cinematic experience of the year with “Meg 2: The Trench” – where the depths of the ocean are matched only by the heights of sheer, unstoppable excitement!

Warner Bros. Pictures and CMC Pictures present “Meg 2: The Trench,” with Statham and Jing headlining an ensemble cast that also includes Sophia Cai (“The Meg”), Page Kennedy (“The Meg”), Sergio Peris-Mencheta (“Rambo: Last Blood”), Skyler Samuels (“The Gifted”), and Cliff Curtis (“Avatar” franchise).
“Meg 2: The Trench” is directed by Ben Wheatley (“In the Earth,” “Free Fire”), from a screenplay by Jon Hoeber & Erich Hoeber (“The Meg,” “Transformers: Rise of the Beasts”) and Dean Georgaris (“The Meg,” “Lara Croft: Toom Raider – The Cradle of Life”), and a screen story by Dean Georgaris and Jon Hoeber & Erich Hoeber, based on the novel The Trench by Steve Alten. The film is produced by Lorenzo di Bonaventura (“The Meg,” “Bumblebee”) and Belle Avery (“The Meg,” “Before the Devil Knows You’re Dead”), and executive produced by Jason Statham, Cate Adams, Ruigang Li, Catherine Xujun Ying, Wu Jing, E. Bennett Walsh, Erik Howsam, Gerald R. Molen and Randy Greenberg. 

Joining director Wheatley behind the camera are director of photography Haris Zambarloukous (“Belfast,” “Murder on the Orient Express”), production designer Chris Lowe (“The Gray Man,” “No Time to Die”) and editor Jonathan Amos (“Baby Driver,” “Paddington 2”). The visual effects supervisor is Pete Bebb (“Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them,” “Inception”), and costume designer is Lindsay Pugh (“The Matrix Resurrections,” “Krypton”). The music is by Harry Gregson-Williams (“The Meg,” “The Martian”).

Warner Bros. Pictures and CMC Pictures present, in association with DF Pictures, a di Bonaventura/Apelles Entertainment, Inc. production, a Ben Wheatley film, “Meg 2: The Trench.” It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in theaters in North America on August 4, 2023 and internationally beginning 02 August 2023.

snippet.description:

Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. snippet.title: Should you get Samsung Odyssey Ark for your gaming? #LiveTheGame
snippet.description:
Link :- https://www.samsung.com/in/monitors/gaming/odyssey-ark-g97nb-55-inch-ls55bg970nwxxl/


Fellow gamers, if you are as serious about gaming as I am, then don’t miss the Odyssey Ark, the next in gaming evolution.

It is the world’s first 55’ inch 1000R curved screen, which provides larger-than-life gaming sessions. With the all-encompassing Sound Dome Tech and the incredible 4K resolution on the curved screen, maximize immersion. You can use its Flex Move Screen to move and resize content as you want. It won’t compromise the picture quality. On top of this, the 1ms response time will ensure nothing breaks your gaming flow. Get this terrific monitor and set it up yourself easily.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3766 - 9 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3766: Bhide Ki Sharamnak News
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide tells Madhavi about Tapu and Sonu being together, but Madhavi denies his claims. He shows him the love letter card given by Tapu to Sonu and the red rose which symbolizes love and passion. Bhide decides to visit Jethalal at his shop, but Madhavi stops him and tells him about the presence of Nattu Kaka and Bagha in the shop. Later, Bhide calls Jetha and tells him that he is going to give him shocking news which will bring embarrassment to him. The statement by Bhide makes Jethalal nervous and he gets worried about Bhide's complaint. Follow along to discover more!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3766, 9 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Why is Manipur violence dangerous for India? | Manipur riots explained | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, we will explore the causes and consequences of the 2023 Manipur violence, an ongoing ethnic clash between the Hindu Meitei people and Christian tribal Kuki people in India’s north-eastern state of Manipur. The violence erupted on 3 May 2023 during the “Tribal Solidarity March” called by the All Tribal Student Union Manipur (ATSUM) to protest the granting of reservations to the majority Meitei community1. The violence killed at least 60 people, and injured at least a further 230. It also resulted in the burning of 25 churches and the displacement of 23,000 people. The Indian Army and the Assam Rifles were deployed to restore law and order, and a shoot-at-sight order was issued in some areas. Internet services were also suspended for five days. We will examine the historical and political background of the conflict, which involves land rights, religious differences, and identity politics. We will also look at the current situation and the prospects for peace and reconciliation in this volatile region.

Please like, share, and subscribe to our channel for more videos on current affairs and social issues. Thank you for watching!

#Manipur #NorthEast #abhiandniyu

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 681 & 682 | Recap
snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 681 & 682 | Recap

Harleen notices Ekam falling for Nehmat again and requests Sartaj to take her home. Meanwhile, Nehmat confesses the truth to Ekam and apologises for hurting him. How will Ekam react to it?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Rajauri Encounter: सिद्धांत छेत्री की 2 महीने पहले हुई थी शादी, बलिदान की खबर सुनकर पत्नी हुई बेहोश
snippet.description:
#rajouriencounter  #indianarmy  #siddhantchhetri #jammukashmir 

Rajauri Encounter: सरहद पर देश की सुरक्षा यूहीं नहीं हो जाती…इसके लिए जान की बाज़ी लगानी पड़ती है. हमारे देश के कितने ही बहादुर जवान हर पल हमें और आप लोगों को महफूज़ रखने के लिए Border पर सीना तान कर मुस्तैद खड़े हैं. इस मुस्तैदी की कीमत कभी देश के लिए जान देकर भी चुकानी पड़ती है. Jammu Kashmir के Rajauri में शुक्रवार को ऐसा ही हुआ. जहां देश ने अपने पांच वीर सैनिकों को हमेशा के लिए खो दिया. इन्हीं में से एक थे West Bengal के Siddhant Chhetri..Indian Army में कार्यरत दार्जिलिंग के रहने वाले राइफलमैन सिद्धांत छेत्री…जो कि 9 पैरा कमांडो थे…उनकी बलिदान देने की खबर से पूरे दार्जिलिंग में शोक की लहर दौड़ गई. पूरा परिवार शोक में डूब चुका है.

hi.title: Rajauri Encounter: सिद्धांत छेत्री की 2 महीने पहले हुई थी शादी, बलिदान की खबर सुनकर पत्नी हुई बेहोश
hi.description:
#rajouriencounter  #indianarmy  #siddhantchhetri #jammukashmir 

Rajauri Encounter: सरहद पर देश की सुरक्षा यूहीं नहीं हो जाती…इसके लिए जान की बाज़ी लगानी पड़ती है. हमारे देश के कितने ही बहादुर जवान हर पल हमें और आप लोगों को महफूज़ रखने के लिए Border पर सीना तान कर मुस्तैद खड़े हैं. इस मुस्तैदी की कीमत कभी देश के लिए जान देकर भी चुकानी पड़ती है. Jammu Kashmir के Rajauri में शुक्रवार को ऐसा ही हुआ. जहां देश ने अपने पांच वीर सैनिकों को हमेशा के लिए खो दिया. इन्हीं में से एक थे West Bengal के Siddhant Chhetri..Indian Army में कार्यरत दार्जिलिंग के रहने वाले राइफलमैन सिद्धांत छेत्री…जो कि 9 पैरा कमांडो थे…उनकी बलिदान देने की खबर से पूरे दार्जिलिंग में शोक की लहर दौड़ गई. पूरा परिवार शोक में डूब चुका है.

snippet.title: Dooramvellake Music Video | Neha Chowdary | Vinay Shanmukh | Vijay Vikranth | Sampath | ShreeMani
snippet.description:
#VinayShanmukh #DooramVellake #nehachowdary #vijayvikranth
We are excited to present the much awaited music video for #DooramVellake.

Composed by Ajay Arasada, Lyrics penned by Shreemani,
Vocals by Lipsika and Yazin Nizar.

Starring #nehachowdary & #vijayvikranth. 
#DooramVellake is the journey of two young lovers, where the boy and girl express their contrasting feelings raising out of the distance between them.

Directed & Shot - Vinay Shanmukh https://www.instagram.com/vinayshanmukh/
Produced by - RS Dream Works Media/Maka Sampath Kumar 
https://www.instagram.com/rsdreamworksmedia/
https://www.instagram.com/sampath.insta/
Cast - Neha Chowdary & Vijay Vikranth
https://www.instagram.com/nehachowdary.25/
https://www.instagram.com/vijayvikranth23/
Music - Ajay Arasada 
https://www.instagram.com/arasada.ajay/
Lyrics - Shreemani
https://www.instagram.com/shreelyricist/
Vocals - Lipsika & Yazin Nizar
https://www.instagram.com/lipsikabhashyam/
https://www.instagram.com/yazin_nizar/
Production Designer - Mohan Reddy
https://www.instagram.com/mohanreddy42/
Associate Cameraman - Prakash Karanam
https://www.instagram.com/prakashkaranam_07/
Associate Director - Ajay Pangoji
Keyboards : Satya 
Flute : Pramod Umapathi 
Violin : Sandilya Pisapati
Children Chorus 
Mix & Master :  : Vinay Kumar  
Studios : Everest Studios, AjA Records
Recording Engineer : Rakesh


Enjoy the visuals of the song and feel the lyrics.

పల్లవి 
F 
ఎవరు ఎవరు చెప్పగలరు 
ఎదురు చూపు తీపి 
ఎదురు చూసే ప్రేమ కబురునడుగు 
నిమిషమాపి 

చూపదా కనులలోన దాచుకున్న కలలవాన 
ఎంతగా వేచి వేచి కలుసుకుంటే అంత తీయన 

M 
ఓ ఓ 
ఎన్ని నాళ్ళని అంతులేని ఈ ఎదురుచూపులింక చాలే 
వీక్షణం వేధించి చంపేంతలా 
దూరమెళ్ళకే దూరమవ్వకే 
దగ్గరవ్వు నాకివ్వాళే 

నిన్నే చూసే రోజేదని 
రోజూ ఆలోచిస్తూ ఉంటానే
నిన్ను చూడకుంటే ఊపిరాడదే అంటోందే ప్రాణం 
ఒక్క నిమిషమైన వేచి ఉండదే 
గుండెని ఏం చైడం 
F 
ఎవరు ఎవరు చెప్పగలరు 
ఎదురు చూపు తీపి 
ఎదురు చూసే కబురునడుగు 
నిమిషమాపి
చరణం 

Charanam :
M 
ఏకాంత వేళల్లో జారే వెన్నెల 
నీ జంట ఎక్కడంటూ అడిగే నన్నిలా 

ఇన్నాళ్ల మౌనం మాటాడమందే 
నీతోటి లోకం చూడలనుందే 
వందేళ్ల కాలం కరిగిపోకముందే 
నీతో ప్రయాణం మొదలు పెట్టమందే

F 
ఎవరు ఎవరు చెప్పగలరు 
ఎదురు చూపు తీపి 
గుండెలోన బాధ కబురు 
కళ్ళలోన చూపి 
ఇంతగా ప్రాణమిచ్చే ప్రేమ ఉంటే ఆగుతానా 
కొత్తగా రెక్కలేవో కట్టుకొచ్చి 
నిన్నిలా చేరనా.

The song is available on all music streaming platforms
1. Spotify 
https://spoti.fi/3NNG2b9
2. Apple Music 
https://apple.co/44CaHya
3. Amazon Music 
https://amzn.to/44AEXtt
4. Hungama Music 
https://bit.ly/3HNyYYr
5. Youtube Music
https://bit.ly/3M6iZr9

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3765 - 8 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 37645: Tapu Ka Proposal
--------------------------------------------------------
The parents of a girl named Sonu come to see Bhide and tell him how their daughter eloped with her boyfriend. Bhide is anxious about Sonu because of this. When Madhavi receives a call from Anjali informing her of the Mahila Mandali meeting, she makes haste there. Bhide is instructed to wait since Madhavi is expecting a significant mango delivery. Sonu doesn't answer the phone when Bhide tries to call her, so he sets out to find her. Bhide eventually makes it to Lover's Park, where he sees Tapu bending over and giving Sonu a red rose. Follow along to discover more!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3765, 8 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000219280

localized.description:
વાર્તા એક હૃદય તૂટેલા પ્રેમીની આસપાસ ફરે છે જે તેના જીવનમાં ફરી પાછા ફરવાની રાહ જોઈ રહી છે. જુઓ રાકેશ બારોટનું નવું બેવફા ગીત "ભુલવા માંગુ હું તને" ફક્ત @SaregamaGujarati પર!

Listen to the best of Rakesh Barot songs only on Saregama Gujarati !
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUzteH3czVO5WMxyPrP2RWK4MMHuCKLwL

Singer: Rakesh Barot, Reshma Thakor
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Chhaya Thakor
Co Artist : Bharat Chaudhari, Sanjay Padnya, Mukesh Bhai, Vipul Bhai 
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema

Lyrics:
એ ભૂલવા માંગુ છું તને
એ ભૂલવા માંગુ છું તને નથી ભુલાતી તારી
બેવફાઈજીવવા ના દેતી કે હોવે હોવે 
બેવફાઈ જીવવા ના દેતી કે હોવે હોવે 
કે હૂતો દૂધ નો દાજેલો છાશ ફૂંકી ફૂંકી પીતો

હે કડવા વેણ બોલ્યા તમે
હે કડવા વેણ બોલ્યા તમે ભલે રે બોલ્યા 
પણ બેવફા બોલવું નતું
કે મને આવું લેબલ લગાડવું નોતું
કે યાદ કરી તમને હું રોતી છોનું છોનું

હે ભૂલવા માંગુ છું તને નથી ભુલાતી તારી
બેવફાઈ જીવવા ના દેતી કે હોવે હોવે 
બેવફાઈ જીવવા ના દેતી કે હોવે હોવે 
કે હૂતો દૂધ નો દાજેલો છાશ ફૂંકી ફૂંકી પીતો

એ ભોળા ચહેરા માં તારા મન ભરમાંણા મારા
જરા એ જોણાવા ના દીધા વિચાર તારા
હો બેવફા કયો છો વાત હોમભળી અધૂરી
જાણી ના પિયુ તમે મારી મજબૂરી

હે ભૂલી જવું તું મને..
હે ભૂલી જવું તું મને ભલે તું ભૂલી પણ કાવતરું કરવું નોતું
એ દાડો મને માંડલિયો બોનધવું નોતું
કે હૂતો દૂધ નો દાજેલો છાશ ફૂંકી ફૂંકી પીતો

એ વેમ કર્યો તો તમે ભલે રે કર્યો પણ આળખોટું નાખવું નોતું
કે પિયુ મને બદનામ કરાવી નોતી
કે યાદ કરી તમને હૂતો છોનું છોનું રોતી
કે હૂતો દૂધ નો દાજેલો છાશ ફૂંકી ફૂંકી પીતો

પ્રેમ કહાની મારી રઈ ગઈ અધૂરી
જિંદગી બેવફા એ કરી નાખી પુરી
જોયા માવતર ની આંખે મેતો આસુંડા
આસુંડા જોઈ મારા બદલાણા મનડા

હે પારકું પાનેતર ઓઢ્યું
હે પારકું પાનેતર ઓઢ્યું મારી બંગડીઓ ફોડાવી નોતી
કે હોવે હોવે બંગડીઓ કઢાવી નોતી
કે હૂતો દૂધ નો દાજેલો છાશ ફૂંકી ફૂંકી પીતો

હે નથી બેવફા કે નથી દગાળી મને મજબૂરી એ મારી નાખી
કે પિયુ મેતો મૉન્યુ માવતર નું કેવું
કે યાદ કરી તમને હૂતો રોતી છોનું છોનું

હે ભૂલવા માંગુ છું તને નથી ભુલાતી તારી
બેવફાઈજીવવા ના દેતી કે હોવે હોવે 
બેવફાઈ જીવવા ના દેતી કે હોવે 
કે હૂતો દૂધ નો દાજેલો છાશ ફૂંકી ફૂંકી પીતો

હે કડવા વેણ બોલ્યા તમે ભલે રે બોલ્યા 
પણ બેવફા બોલવું નતું
કે મને આવું લેબલ લગાડવું નોતું
કે યાદ કરી તમને હું રોતી છોનું છોનું

કે હોવે હૂતો દૂધ નો દાજેલો છાશ ફૂંકી ફૂંકી પીતો
કે યાદ કરી તમને હું રોતી છોનું છોનું

snippet.title: തമിഴ്നാട്ടിലും അരി തേടിയെത്തി അരിക്കൊമ്പൻ; അനുഭവം വിവരിച്ച് മേഘമലക്കാർ  | Arikomban at Tamil Nadu
snippet.description:
ചിന്നക്കനാലിൽ നിന്ന് കാടുകടത്തിയ അരിക്കൊമ്പൻ ഇപ്പോൾ തമ്പടിച്ചിരിക്കുന്നത് തമിഴ്നാട് അതിർത്തി പ്രദേശമായ മേഘമലയിലാണ്. കഴിഞ്ഞ ദിവസം പുലർച്ചെ ഇവിടത്തെ ഇരവുങ്കല്ലാർ എസ്റ്റേറ്റിലെ ഒരു വീട് തള്ളിത്തുറന്ന് അരി എടുക്കുകയും ചെയ്തു. തുമ്പിക്കൈ വീടിനകത്തിട്ട് അരിച്ചാക്ക് തപ്പിയെടുത്ത് കൊണ്ടുപോവുകയായിരുന്നെന്ന് സംഭവത്തിന് ദൃക്സാക്ഷിയായ വീട്ടുടമസ്ഥൻ കറുപ്പസാമി പറയുന്നു.

snippet.title: Shub-Man is now Spider-Man | Pavitr Prabhakar in Spider-Man: Across the SpiderVerse | June 2nd
snippet.description:
Thrilled to have the talented Shubman Gill as the voice of our very own - Indian Spider-Man, Pavitr Prabhakar in Spider-Man: Across the #SpiderVerse. 
Trailer dropping soon! Get ready for some web-slinging action! 🕷️🇮🇳

Releasing in 10 languages all through the country; in English, Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Punjabi, Gujarati, Marathi, Bengali, Kannada & Malayalam 🕸️

Miles Morales returns for the next chapter of the Oscar®-winning Spider-Verse saga, Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse. After reuniting with Gwen Stacy, Brooklyn’s full-time, friendly neighborhood Spider-Man is catapulted across the Multiverse, where he encounters a team of Spider-People charged with protecting its very existence. But when the heroes clash on how to handle a new threat, Miles finds himself pitted against the other Spiders and must redefine what it means to be a hero so he can save the people he loves most.

snippet.description:

भोले बाबा देदे नोट छापन की मशीन | Note Chhapan Ki Machine DJ | New Bholenath Song | Chanda Bhakti 

Title :-  नोट छापन की मशीन || Note Chhapan Ki Machine
Singer :-  Rajesh Singhpuriya, Meenakshi Panchal
Lyrics :- Rajesh Singhpuriya
Artist - Rajesh Singhpuriya, Kalpana Naihra, Mohit, Shalu, Kajal, Ashis
Music :- Rajesh Singhpuriya
Design :- Kuldeep Gaur
Company / Label :- Chanda Bhakti

#note_chhapan_ki_machine #bhole_baba_dede

#rajeshsinghpuriya #notechhapankimasine

Song Lyrics:------------------------------------------------------------
जे भोला बाबा देदे
नोट छप्पन की मशीन
सबकी बजा दूं

जे भोला बाबा देदे
नोट छप्पन की मशीन
सबकी बजा दूं
था दूंगा झरता रे
ग़बरा जा अंबानी टाटा रे

हो बंदर के हाथ में जे रेल पकड़ा दी
बंदर के हाथ में जे रेल पकड़ा दी
वो करदे गा नुक्सान जाने से भगवान
पूछे सबकी जात ने
हो तने रखेगा औकात में

हां

जे भोला बाबा देदे
नोट छप्पन की मशीन
सबकी बजा दूं
था दूंगा झरता रे
जय हो!
ग़बरा जा अंबानी टाटा रे

झुठे सपने देखे जा से
नहीं काम के खाना
भोले की फौज नए लेगी मौज
हमने क्या का घाटा रे
घबराया जा अंबानी टाटा रे


बम बम बम

काला कुत्ता चाहिए माल तने
आईएनजी भूरी ए मिलेगी गाल तने
हा गोरी माई नादान
तने दिया से ज्ञान
नी कर्ण एब के घटा रे
हो ना खत्म होगा आटा रे

बम बम बम!

Je Bhola Baba Deden
Note Chhapan Ki Machine
Sabki Baja Dyu Been


Je Bhola Baba Dede
Note Chhapan Ki Machine
Sabki Baja Dyu Been
Thaa Dyunga Jharrata Re
Ghabra Jaa Ambani Tata Re

 
Ho Bandar Ke Hath Me Je Rail Pakda Di
Bandar Ke Hath Me Je Rail Pakda Di
Wo Karde Ga Nuksaan Jaane Se Bhagwan
Puche Sabki Jaat Ne
Ho Tane Rakhega Aukaat Me

Haan


Je Bhola Baba Dede
Note Chhapan Ki Machine
Sabki Baja Dyu Been
Thaa Dyunga Jharrata Re
Jai Ho
Ghabra Jaa Ambani Tata Re


Jhuthe Sapne Dekhe Jaa Se
Nahi Kamaa Ke Khana
Bhole Ki Fauj Nyue Legi Mauj
Hamne Kya Ka Ghata Re
Ghabraa Ja Ambani Tata Re

Ing Bhuri E Milengi Gaal Tane

Tane Diya Se Gyan

snippet.title: On a BMTC bus, with the incredible women of Bengaluru | Rahul Gandhi | Karnataka
snippet.description:
On a BMTC bus, with the incredible women of Bengaluru | Rahul Gandhi | Karnataka.

Congress' 5 Guarantees

1. GRUHA JYOTHI - 200 units of free electricity every month to every household to help bear bills.

2. GRUHA LAKSHMI - ₹2,000 each month to the female head of every household for sustenance and help in the fight against price rise.

3. ANNA BHAGYA - 10 Kg rice, every month to every member of BPL families. No one in Karnataka will sleep hungry.

4. YUVA NIDHI - ₹3,000 every month to every unemployed graduate for a period of two years. And ₹1,500 to unemployed youths with Diploma. So, during the period they are finding a job, Congress govt will help them with income support.

5. Free bus travel for women in govt buses to ensure they have the freedom to travel without worrying to pay.

The cause of the fire is still unknown, although it is believed to have been sparked by a combination of static electricity and a hydrogen leak. But what was the full story of this accident? snippet.title: NEET 2023 Question Paper Discussion || Physics Wallah || NEET 2023 Answer Key
snippet.description:
Submit Your NEET Application - https://bit.ly/neet_YT
NEET MahaRevision : https://bit.ly/3N3LZ3y


Batch Details : 
- We will cover Botany, Zoology, Physics, Organic Chemistry, Inorganic Chemistry, and Physical Chemistry in One Shot

- One Shot Marathon series will start on Physics wallah - Alakh Pandey Channel on 19th April 2023

- Then, Subject wise Master MCQ Marathon series will be continue on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel on 26th April 2023

- At the end, 5 Live AITS (All India Test Series) Live Discussion on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel

- After NEET 2023 Exam, the Live Paper Discussion will also be scheduled on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel at the same day.

- Lecture notes will be available on NEET Maha Revision 2023 Batch (PW App)

- The complete course will be accessible to all the students until the NEET 2023 Exams

- Marathon Schedule will be provided in the community post of Competition Wallah YT Channel and Announcement section of the PW App


#NEET #PhysicsWallah #NEET2023 #NEETExam #NEETAnswerKey #QuestionPaperDiscussion
